    <!-- author: will@1dao2.com
         date:   2017/10/22

         course table canvas:
         1920 x 1080

         sidebar      table         sidebar
         + ~~~ + ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ + ~~~ +
    week |258px|      1400px        |260px|
         + ~~~ + ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ +     +
         |     |                    |     |
         |Time |    Course Table    |EMPTY|
         |     |                    |     |
           ... |       ...            ...
              2px: divider line

         Table: 7 x 8 => 1400px * 640px

         Course Item: 200px * 80px
         200px = 198px + 2px
         80px  = 78px  + 2px

         Total canvas:
         (258px + 2px + 1400px) * week-height * (2px + 640px)
     -->

